# Cloudflare Pages — root redirects
#
# The app lives at AI-Car-Racer/index.html because ruvectorBridge.js
# statically imports `../vendor/ruvector/...` — the server root has to sit
# one level above AI-Car-Racer/ for that path to resolve. This redirect
# makes the bare Pages URL land on the game instead of a 404 directory
# listing. 302 (not 301) so we can move things later without a cached
# permanent redirect getting in the way.
/  /AI-Car-Racer/index.html  302
